{"tid":471160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"早20秒出車　東京鐵路公司致歉","createTime":"2017-11-17T03:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T06:29:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":368,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"a2eba19d33c2bc11dd0c1a2adb939b1d83f8ec8a","tid":471160,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171117/s00005/cdf016900454f5ed25e88271118441f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171117%2Fs00005%2Fcdf016900454f5ed25e88271118441f7.jpg&h=a7f73a22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本鐵路素以準時聞名世界，東京筑波快線近因列車較原定時間早20秒啓程，發表聲明就誤點向民眾致歉。<br />\n<br />\n誤點發生在當地時間周二（14日）上午9時發生，據悉一列由東京秋葉原開出的列車，在43分40秒駛至千葉縣南流山站，隨後列車提早在44分20秒啓程，比原定時間提早20秒。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指事件是由列車司機沒有詳細查閲時間表所致，強調事後已對這名司機予以再培訓。聲明雖然表明沒有乘客對此投訴，但仍對乘客造成不便致歉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171117/s00005/1510885576570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171117%2Fs00005%2F1510885576570&d=j3GOyvcuxBwnVifK%2BrcsgL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=1e2dce30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171117%2Fs00005%2F1510885576570&h=f70fdcd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171117/s00005/1510885576570</a>"},{"pid":"175f7da5dc8094a0f97f5cc78831e004384f0a9f","tid":471160,"uid":41974,"like":131,"dislike":1,"score":130,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:57:16.000Z","msg":"專業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a76e2ae5d25318d1b3a25f960b138c8033731e","tid":471160,"uid":52215,"like":7,"dislike":141,"score":-134,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:58:39.000Z","msg":"垃圾公司"},{"pid":"9712d6e707cf6fc7d38467dec14321552a16351e","tid":471160,"uid":11254,"like":211,"dislike":0,"score":211,"c