,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T04:59:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171117/s00005/cdf016900454f5ed25e88271118441f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171117%2Fs00005%2Fcdf016900454f5ed25e88271118441f7.jpg&h=a7f73a22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">日本鐵路素以準時聞名世界</span>，東京筑波快線近因列車較原定時間早20秒啓程，發表聲明就誤點向民眾致歉。<br />\n<br />\n誤點發生在當地時間周二（14日）上午9時發生，據悉一列由東京秋葉原開出的列車，在43分40秒駛至千葉縣南流山站，隨後列車提早在44分20秒啓程，比原定時間提早20秒。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指事件是由列車司機沒有詳細查閲時間表所致，強調事後已對這名司機予以再培訓。聲明雖然表明沒有乘客對此投訴，但仍對乘客造成不便致歉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171117/s00005/1510885576570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171117%2Fs00005%2F1510885576570&d=j3GOyvcuxBwnVifK%2BrcsgL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=1e2dce30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171117%2Fs00005%2F1510885576570&h=f70fdcd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171117/s00005/1510885576570</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 準碌鳩咩，一星期翻四日學有三日架車會遲，仲有次趁考試先停個幾鐘車"},{"pid":"d3029f29b03a0a4113219d0087c7d3b44bf92501","tid":471160,"uid":33733,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T04:59:13.000Z","msg":"港鐵表示望住你地係金鐘轉車跑過對面月台時，我關門開車走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e703038050d19886ebddb0b8a556b421318aa9","tid":471160,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T05:00:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>道歉就滿足到班港豬?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點都好過狗鐵唔道歉之餘仲光明正大繼續加價"},{"pid":"822caaa62c4e26c1eecfa3afdacb2abb968a4df4","tid":471160,"uid":86893,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T05